rows.label: qst300107_msg001
rows.name: It's a Dobus Ansel! [ML:Dash ]This is bad.

rows.label: qst300107_msg002
rows.name:
They love Mokmo Onions,
so they'll sniff them out
and attack in a swarm.

rows.label: qst300107_msg003
rows.name:
You can wipe out the whole
swarm, but if you defeat the
leader, they'll flee...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst300107_msg004
rows.name:
Vandham-san always took them
out so quickly that I can't
tell which one the leader is.

rows.label: qst300107_msg005
rows.name:
We'll just have to take them down
one by one until we find it!
